These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby, climbing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Pet     | ferret | mouse    | fish   |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | climbing | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller, horror
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | fanta   | tea  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | fantasy | horror    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, canadian, japanese
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, ferret
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the american is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
4. the japanese is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | american |
| Pet           | horse    | ferret     | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, papaya, grapefruit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, skateboarding
1. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
3. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food    | grapefruit | raspberry     | papaya   |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | lacrosse | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, colombian
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, van, tram
1. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the tram is the mexican##1
3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | colombian   |
| Transport     | van | tram    | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, singing, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, funk, salsa
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | singing | hiking | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | funk   | salsa        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, manager, architect
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Job     | librarian | architect    | manager |
| Sport   | ice-hockey      | water-polo | weightlifting             |

