.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, writing, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, bartender, firefighter
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | writing  | collecting    |
| Job     | firefighter   | social-worker | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, cola
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, helicopter, trike
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk       | iced-tea   | cola |
| Transport   | helicopter | train | trike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, coach, scientist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, disco, funk
1. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of funk and the fan of disco##2
4. the coach is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | chef | coach | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | jazz      | funk    |

