.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, water
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, dutch
1. the colombian is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | water   | coffee     | soy-milk      |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian | japanese |

