.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, grapes, cucumber
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, airplane
1. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
2. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
4. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Food        | cranberry | grapes | cucumber |
| Transport   | car  | quad-bike         | airplane   |

