.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, r&b, metal
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal          | r&b     | techno  |
| Sport         | cricket | rugby | volleyball |

