.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, superhero
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk  | lemonade         |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | sports | superhero |

