.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-15::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, bartender, fisherman
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, ice-hockey, cricket
1. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
3. the fisherman is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job     | fisherman | bartender   | accountant   |
| Sport   | handball | ice-hockey | cricket |

