3. the turkish is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality   | polish | brazilian       | turkish |
| Sport         | basketball | surfing | water-polo |

