.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, hamster
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | chess | puzzles |
| Pet     | hamster  | lizard    | chinchilla    |

