.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, classical
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | dubstep | classical  |
| Transport     | jet-ski | skateboard   | quad-bike |

 